        public void setCompRes(java.lang.String path,
                       java.util.List<CompRes> compres)
        Set Competition Result. It is a help method.
        Parameters:
        compres - The List of Competition Results you want to go to the file.
        path - The Path to the .txt File. Hand it the FilePath In the format "Junior" or "Senior" + Disciplin "BackCrawl", "Crawl", "Butterfly", "Breast". Example if you want Junior Backcrawl, hand it "JuniorBackCrawl".
